item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Birds of Prey: Complete Series in HD (Digital)
item.description:
Hey all! Was wondering if anyone would be kind enough to share an upload of the 2002-2003 series Birds of Prey in HD.

Looks like WB made HD masters for digital viewing/purchase, with it available in 720p on TubiTV and "HD" (I assume is 1080p) on Itunes, Amazon, and Vudu.

Would prefer the 1080p version, but 720p would suffice.

Any help would be appreciated, since the DVDs are letterboxed widescreen (4 black bars on image) and the series has never gotten a physical release in an HD format.
item.author: goldmotel
